text:
# Group inheritance
#
# Any inherited groups prefixed with a g: are global groups
# and are inherited from the GlobalGroups.yml.
#
# Groups without the g: prefix are groups local to this world
# and are defined in the this groups.yml file.
#
# Local group inheritances define your promotion tree when using 'manpromote/mandemote'

groups:
  Helper:
    default: false
    permissions:
    - -nte.member
    - essentials.kick
    - essentials.mute
    - essentials.tempban
    - nte.helper
    - staff.chat.clear
    - staff.chat.slow
    - staff.chat.toggle
    - staff.warn
    inheritance:
    - member
    info:
      build: true
      prefix: '&f[&e&lHelper&f]&e '
      suffix: ''
  Moderator:
    default: false
    permissions:
    - -nte.builder
    - essentials.fly
    - factionfly.ally
    - factionfly.enemy
    - factionfly.neutral
    - factionfly.own
    - factionfly.safezone
    - factionfly.warzone
    - factionfly.wild
    - factionsfly.allow
    - ffly.bypass
    - ffly.fly
    - ffly.others
    - nte.moderator
    inheritance:
    - builder
    - g:groupmanager_moderator
    - g:bukkit_moderator
    - g:essentials_moderator
    - g:towny_moderator
    - g:vanish_moderator
    info:
      build: true
      prefix: '&f[&3&lModerator&f]&3 '
      suffix: ''
  Owner:
    default: false
    permissions:
    - +vanish.effects.toggle.all
    - -nte.admin
    - -vanish.effects.*
    - '*'
    - nte.owner
    inheritance:
    - admin
    info:
      build: true
      prefix: '&b[&4&lOwner&b]&e '
      suffix: ''
  Zeus:
    default: false
    permissions:
    - -nte.poseidon
    - -essentials.kits.poseidon
    - -essentials.kits.poseidon1
    - essentials.kits.zeus
    - essentials.kits.zeus1
    - essentials.repair
    - essentials.repair.enchanted
    - jellylegs.enable
    - nte.zeus
    inheritance:
    - g:groupmanager_default
    - g:bukkit_default
    - g:essentials_default
    - g:towny_default
    - poseidon
    info:
      build: true
      prefix: '&f[&bZeus&f]&b '
      suffix: ''
  Poseidon:
    default: false
    permissions:
    - -nte.god
    - -essentials.kits.god
    - -essentials.kits.god1
    - essentials.back
    - essentials.kits.poseidon
    - essentials.kits.poseidon1
    - essentials.nick.color
    - nightvision.enable
    - nte.poseidon
    - waterbreathing.enable
    inheritance:
    - g:groupmanager_default
    - g:bukkit_default
    - g:essentials_default
    - g:towny_default
    - god
    info:
      build: true
      prefix: '&f[&9Poseidon&f]&9 '
      suffix: ''
  Builder:
    default: false
    permissions:
    - nte.builder
    inheritance:
    - g:essentials_builder
    - g:towny_builder
    - member
    info:
      build: true
      prefix: '&f[&e&lBuilder&f]&e '
      suffix: ''
  Youtube:
    default: false
    permissions:
    - -nte.demi
    - essentials.feed
    - essentials.kits.demigod
    - essentials.kits.demigod1
    - nte.yt
    inheritance:
    - g:groupmanager_default
    - g:bukkit_default
    - g:essentials_default
    - g:towny_default
    - demi-god
    info:
      build: true
      prefix: '&f[&4&lYou&f&lTube&f]&f '
      suffix: ''
  Admin:
    default: false
    permissions:
    - -nte.moderator
    - nte.admin
    inheritance:
    - moderator
    - g:groupmanager_admin
    - g:bukkit_admin
    - g:essentials_admin
    - g:towny_admin
    - g:vanish_admin
    info:
      build: true
      prefix: '&f[&6&lAdmin&f]&6 '
      suffix: ''
  Member:
    default: true
    permissions:
    - -bukkit.command.kill
    - -bukkit.command.plugins
    - -essentials.plugin
    - -bukkit.command.help
    - -worldedit.calc
    - -bukkit.command.me
    - coins.creeper
    - coins.feed
    - coins.gap
    - coins.hopper
    - coins.nick
    - coins.night
    - coins.obsidian
    - coins.rank
    - coins.tnt
    - essentials.balance
    - essentials.balancetop
    - essentials.delhome
    - essentials.help
    - essentials.helpop
    - essentials.home
    - essentials.ignore
    - essentials.info
    - essentials.kit
    - essentials.kits.food
    - essentials.kits.list
    - essentials.kits.starter
    - essentials.list
    - essentials.mail
    - essentials.motd
    - essentials.msg
    - essentials.pay
    - essentials.r
    - essentials.realname
    - essentials.rules
    - essentials.sethome
    - essentials.sethome.multiple.default
    - essentials.signs.buy.use
    - essentials.signs.sell.use
    - essentials.spawn
    - essentials.suicide
    - essentials.tpa
    - essentials.tpaccept
    - essentials.tpahere
    - essentials.tpdeny
    - essentials.warp
    - essentials.warp.list
    - essentials.warps.Crates
    - essentials.warps.Donate
    - essentials.warps.Enchant
    - essentials.warps.Grinder
    - essentials.warps.Shop
    - essentials.warps.Staff
    - modifyworld.*
    - nte.member
    - shopguiplus.shop
    - shopguiplus.shops.blocks
    - shopguiplus.shops.decor
    - shopguiplus.shops.drops
    - shopguiplus.shops.farming
    - shopguiplus.shops.miscellanous
    - shopguiplus.shops.ores
    - shopguiplus.shops.potions
    - shopguiplus.shops.raiding
    - shopguiplus.shops.spawners
    - silkspawners.info
    - silkspawners.place.*
    - silkspawners.silkdrop.*
    - silkspawners.use.buy
    - warpgui.menu
    - wildtp.wild
    inheritance:
    - g:groupmanager_default
    - g:bukkit_default
    - g:essentials_default
    - g:towny_default
    info:
      build: true
      prefix: '&f[&7Member&f]&7 '
      suffix: ''
  God:
    default: false
    permissions:
    - -nte.demi
    - -essentials.kits.demigod
    - -essentials.kits.demigod1
    - essentials.kits.god
    - essentials.kits.god1
    - essentials.nick
    - nte.god
    inheritance:
    - g:groupmanager_default
    - g:bukkit_default
    - g:essentials_default
    - g:towny_default
    - demi-god
    info:
      build: true
      prefix: '&f[&cGod&f]&c '
      suffix: ''
  Demi-God:
    default: false
    permissions:
    - -nte.member
    - essentials.enderchest
    - essentials.feed
    - essentials.hat
    - essentials.kits.demigod

    - nte.demi

    - g:groupmanager_default
    - g:bukkit_default
    - g:essentials_default
    - g:towny_default
    - member
    info:
      build: true
      prefix: '&f[&aDemi-God&f]&a '
      suffix: ''
